CODING STYLE

	Variables declaration in the pkgmk's code:

	+----------------+-------------------------------------------+
	| ${var}, ${VAR} | Global variable. External, declared in    |
	|                | sourced files like Pkgfile or pkgmk.conf. |
	+----------------+-------------------------------------------+
	| $VAR           | Internal, global variable.                |
	+----------------+-------------------------------------------+
	| $__VAR         | Local variable.                           |
	+----------------+-------------------------------------------+

End of file.
